  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示核心模块在同步任务结束后如何安全地提交事务并发布事件。关键点是Security_OAuth2和Security_ZeroTrust的防护层级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：kikwi-core作为入口，携带OAuth2认证；然后进入UnitOfWork的零信任环境。事务提交时还需要入侵检测对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "kikwi-core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，UnitOfWork初始化时要带上Security_IntrusionDetection参数。另外注意同步任务阶段只有Core自己执行，还没涉及数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Executa tarefas síncronas"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出Core的自循环，标注同步任务。然后Core创建UoW，用虚线箭头表示accumula变更的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core-Core",
        "Core-UoW",
        "Acumula alterações"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在同步块结束的位置加一个注释说明\"Fim do bloco síncrono\"，这样边界清晰。接下来Core要调用Repository的commit方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over Core",
        "Fim do bloco síncrono",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加注释。现在画出Core到Repository的同步调用，Repository再激活MongoDB开启事务。这里用加号表示激活对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core-+Repository",
        "Repository-+MongoDB",
        "INICIAR TRANSAÇÃO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用加号。MongoDB内部要有三步：更新ProcessInstance、处理ExecutableTasks的创建删除、还有把criticalEvents写入event_outbox。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MongoDB-MongoDB",
        "Atualiza ProcessInstance",
        "Cria/Apaga ExecutableTasks",
        "Insere 'criticalEvents'"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三步都画好了，用自循环表示内部操作。事务完成后MongoDB返回给Repository，Repository再返回给Core。这里用虚线箭头表示返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MongoDB---Repository",
        "Repository---Core",
